    "originContent": "## Architecture & Design Principles",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "플러그인은 다음의 주요 원칙들을 구현합니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "5BxOAlC7GdcpEwdOwk5YrAoR7HLIqUpmJymoCUCbxH4=",
    "originContent": "The plugin implements several key principles:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- **초전문화(Ultra-Specialization)** — 각 에이전트는 명확한 책임과 정의된 인계 절차를 가짐"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "Y0Vv/GjhW4pkk1PZRjtde0izdI3t29jISS6WjEe2bBw=",
    "originContent": "- **Ultra-Specialization** — Each agent has one clear responsibility with defined handoffs",
    "translatedContent": "- **모델 층화(Model Stratification)** — 아키텍처용 Opus(최상의 추론), 구현용 Inherit(비용 효율적), 유틸리티용 Haiku(빠름)"
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "GQ9RFUqSMMSeb+7tfWjaABZdqx91DSjrJrphtpQyhIg=",
    "originContent": "- **Model Stratification** — Opus for architecture (best reasoning), Inherit for implementation (cost-effective), Haiku for utilities (fast)",
    "translatedContent": "- **로컬 우선(Local-First)** — 기본값은 SQLite 및 UserDefaults, SwiftData 또는 Core Data는 사용하지 않음"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "1nPmJLygTfGn7wa/G6nzrDKoQp0MuHNcZmnjY1ZjRpM=",
    "originContent": "- **Local-First** — Default to SQLite and UserDefaults, never SwiftData or Core Data",
    "translatedContent": "- **모던 스위프트 전용(Modern Swift Only)** — Swift 6.2 및 엄격한 동시성, 폐기된 API 미사용"
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "so1UOdyhC+TDp0R+HNW83GfegPAKU5Naclh0U+3By0U=",
    "originContent": "- **Modern Swift Only** — Swift 6.2 with strict concurrency, no deprecated APIs",
    "translatedContent": "- **읽기 전용 기획(Read-Only Planning)** — 기획 에이전트는 코드 수정 불가, 명확한 분리 보장"
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "CmxFyil5LOM+DAtsTJoXvZ+ao+yoJRWX7n+Ragdrjbg=",
    "originContent": "- **Read-Only Planning** — Planning agents cannot modify code, ensuring clear separation",
    "translatedContent": "- **기획 파일 조정(Plan File Coordination)** — 에이전트들은 `docs/plans/<feature>.md`를 통해 상태 공유"
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "2atdJWxR7+3cDfQvxlJhCNBvb30ABO5wxwQYmP7zjHs=",
    "originContent": "- **Plan File Coordination** — Agents share state via `docs/plans/<feature>.md`",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "아키텍처 세부사항, 워크플로우 다이어그램, 인계 모델은 [plugins/swift-engineering/README.md](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/johnrogers/claude-swift-engineering/main/plugins/swift-engineering/README.md) 참고."
  },
